  <brief_title>Effects of a Gum Gel Intended to Treat Signs and Symptoms of Teething</brief_title>
  <official_title>Retrospective Analysis of the Effects of a Gum Gel Intended to Treat Signs and Symptoms of Teething in Infants</official_title>
